1. U *vikend* sam obično u šetnji sa prijateljima. (On weekends I usually take a walk with my friends.)
2. *Vikend* je moj najdraži deo nedelje. (Weekend is my favorite part of the week.)
3. Nedeljom uveče uglavnom odmaram za *vikend*. (On Sunday evenings I usually rest for the weekend.)
4. Dan pre *vikenda* obično obaveštavam ljude o događaju. (The day before the weekend I usually inform people about an event.)
5. *Vikendom* često putujem po Evropi. (On weekends I often travel around Europe.)